- **Waste Management, Inc.**: Waste Management, Inc. offers integrated medical waste management solutions to healthcare facilities, pharmacies, and laboratories. The company utilizes advanced technologies for efficient waste treatment and disposal, catering to the evolving needs of the healthcare industry.

